WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'MultiCon' is a game where you try to match various shapes by
rotating links connected to tiles on the board. Complete each
shape in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

FEATURES
--------

-Simple installation: just run the game and play!

-25 puzzles to play with.

-Small package, the Lha archive is smaller than 50K, so it
 doesn't take ages to download :)

-The game plays on the Workbench screen and its window is
 resizeable.

